# deepMinMax

- _deepMinMax(c)_

Equivalent to `deepMin` and `deepMax` of the collection _c_.

At a `List`:

```
>>> [8 1 6 3 5 7 4 9 2].deepMinMax
[1 9]
```

At a 3×3 matrix:

```
>>> [8 1 6; 3 5 7; 4 9 2].deepMinMax
[1 9]
```

* * *

See also: deepMax, deepMin, deepInjectInto, min, max

Categories: Testing
